text: Yaroslav Catraio João de Aguiar, nicknamed Jaro, (born 11 June 1985) is an Angolan handball player for Interclube and the Angolan national team. He participated at the 2017 World Men's Handball Championship.2017 World Championship roster ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Angolan male handball players
